title: Cleveland police officer accused of biting woman during argument, stopping her from leaving house
text:
Cleveland police officer accused of biting woman during argument, stopping her from leaving house 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
A Cleveland police officer is accused of biting a woman during an argument, then trying to stop her from leaving the house where it happened...
